00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:03.010
Go where your users
are, the living room.

00:00:03.010 --> 00:00:05.390
Google Cast lets users
project their favorite apps

00:00:05.390 --> 00:00:08.730
from Android, iOS, and the
web right on to their TV.

00:00:08.730 --> 00:00:13.090
Android TV turns a TV into an
Android device, only bigger.

00:00:13.090 --> 00:00:15.610
The Android TV and Google
Cast development course

00:00:15.610 --> 00:00:18.577
from Udacity, built in
collaboration with Google,

00:00:18.577 --> 00:00:20.660
will teach you how to
extend your existing Android

00:00:20.660 --> 00:00:24.100
app to work with both these
living room technologies.

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.550
Take this course to learn
how to add a big screen

00:00:26.550 --> 00:00:29.490
cinematic experience
to your mobile app.

00:00:29.490 --> 00:00:32.130
It's easy because Google
provides the libraries that

00:00:32.130 --> 00:00:34.580
do the heavy lifting for you.

